List 3 major roles that should be included to cover the real-world scenario in this domain comprehensively.
For each role, specify the likely disciplinary background (e.g., Human-Computer Interaction, Computer Science, Management, etc.).
For each role, briefly describe what kinds of issues or concerns this role is most likely to pay attention to during the annotation process.

